{"tid":528963,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日傳奇第2季","createTime":"2018-01-14T11:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T17:50:49.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f19b943f801685ed49f3e23fe443c1921717832d","tid":528963,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3f0da4ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a932e974\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c409f2e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png%3Alarge&h=e6451025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於時間領主總部摧毀，傳奇們被迫擔負起修復歷史的使命。然而他們也擔心時俠的警告，傳奇們發現Damien Darhk於1942年的時候企圖發射核武炸毀紐約。<br />\n<br />\n而Damien Darhk更與逆閃電及黑箭等組成「末日軍團」。逆閃電協助末日軍團的目的就是要防止神速力怪物的追捕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=dadce9e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=11Cbln4b%2BmRSnBXOWXylkhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6ce5935c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288fd99121f48904e2da823330b9c189acad9709","tid":528963,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aabf4b930acca63e5edea1e393d8172aeccbf2d","tid":528963,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65e9d74177cdf564942090e20975a14039cc55a","tid":528963,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77faa4c46377da2a9ff408215dbec8679ff1caf","tid":528963,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /